Reasoning: 
1. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on text mining and natural language processing of Instagram data. 
2. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is also likely as the paper involves analyzing images on Instagram. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is another possible category as the paper deals with extracting information from unstructured text data. 
4. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper uses weak supervision and generative modeling to train a deep clothing classifier. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing both text and images on Instagram.
